{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"c07aca6b-11c6-4872-ae9a-ac3645350f50","content":"Good news — with .NET 10 SDK, `dotnet test` uses Microsoft Testing Platform **by default**. You **no longer need `TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport`** — that property was only required in .NET 9 SDK to opt in to MTP support. In .NET 10, it's built-in.\n\nYou should remove that property:","toolRequests":[{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01WX4Hshq5SyG7UkpucsQqYa","name":"report_intent","arguments":{"intent":"Removing obsolete property"},"type":"function"},{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01GCGzA8iSmE24VgqTeeUmfj","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-e736912291e245408c1c4dc65c323f75/TestProject.csproj","old_str":"    <EnableMSTestRunner>true</EnableMSTestRunner>\n    <TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>true</TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>","new_str":"    <EnableMSTestRunner>true</EnableMSTestRunner>"},"type":"function","intentionSummary":"edit the file at /tmp/sv-e736912291e245408c1c4dc65c323f75/TestProject.csproj."}],"interactionId":"0d442e3e-b38e-4f6f-ad15-e3d49f214383","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user is on .NET 10 SDK (10.0.100) and wants to know about native MTP support. Let me provide accurate information.\n\nIn .NET 10, `dotnet test` natively supports Microsoft Testing Platform (MTP) without needing the `TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport` property. Starting with .NET 10 SDK, MTP is the default test runner when you use `dotnet test`, so that property is no longer needed.\n\nLet me verify this understanding and help them update their project file.\n\nKey points:\n- .NET 10 SDK has native MTP support in `dotnet test` - it's the default\n\n\n- The `TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport` property was specifically for .NET 9 to enable MTP through `dotnet test`, but it's now obsolete in .NET 10\n- `EnableMSTestRunner` is still required if they want to generate a standalone test executable\n- They should remove `TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport` from their project file","outputTokens":541,"requestId":"0C03:2B0E8:234D2E:296641:69F005C8"},"id":"592b243e-620f-47ca-9987-a216cfd2a677","timestamp":"2026-04-28T00:56:50.557Z","parentId":"0e6a1364-ac8f-444a-9a39-2ada15af6e12"}
